May be freely distributed under the MIT license.

To suggest a feature, report a bug, or general discussion:

  - http://github.com/andrzejsliwa/couch-watch/issues/
  - http://github.com/andrzejsliwa/couch-watch/wiki/

Related projects:

  - https://github.com/andrzejsliwa/couch-watch-js - CouchWatch JavaScript Client
  - https://github.com/andrzejsliwa/couch-watch-rb - CouchWatch Ruby Client

Installation & first run:

  $ git clone git://github.com/andrzejsliwa/couch-watch.git
  $ cd couch-watch
  $ git submodule update --init
  $ bundle install
  $ cp .couchapprc.example .couchapprc  # customize .couchpprc here
  $ soca push  # or ./autopush.watchr
